00:00:38.850 --> 00:00:41.970
He reiterates that he's not diminishing
Sony's performance claims and

00:00:41.970 --> 00:00:44.070
wasn't trying to be arrogant or
dismissive.

00:00:44.070 --> 00:00:46.280
And that only great
games are what matters.

00:00:46.280 --> 00:00:50.010
